{"tid":926011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠再售中國資產   5年賺1.44億美元","createTime":"2018-12-03T06:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T15:57:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":179,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"83b0a7a57ca327c855896253a534117db8c4680b","tid":926011,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/03/4/5612993.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F03%2F4%2F5612993.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=8bd6535a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港首富李嘉誠又拋售了一處中國大陸物業，以人民幣25.6億元（約3.68億美元）的價格把北京京通羅斯福廣場全部權益，整體打包賣給領展房地產投資信託基金，僅五年光景，扣掉建設等成本，李嘉誠淨賺人民幣10億元（約1.44億美元）。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊新聞報導，京通羅斯福廣場位於通州區梨園鎮九棵樹中街9號，前身是金成中心，2013年香港長江實業集團旗下新加坡ARA資產管理，以總價2.8億美元收購了該項目，重新改造裝修後更名為京通羅斯福廣場，於2014年開業。<br />\n<br />\n其實李嘉誠早在2013年8月開始，就大舉拋售大陸房產，僅2014年就在南京、北京、上海相繼出售三個辦公大樓，累計套現人民幣97.8億元（約14億美元）。<br />\n<br />\n2016年李嘉誠以人民幣200億（約28.73億美元）賣掉上海世紀匯，而2017年更是把香港中環中心以港幣402億元（51.4億美元）的高價賣掉。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠賣掉香港中環中心時，其實租金一直在上漲，是全球最高租金的地方；目前大陸最高租金的地方是廣州珠江新城，但中環的租金是珠江新城的六倍。<br />\n<br />\n香港中環中心建成至今已運作了20年，是香港的地標之一，李嘉誠擁有75%的權益，大廈每年的租金就有港幣7億元，但李嘉誠賣出後得到港幣402億元，這樣的收入更加豐厚。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠是精明的商人，永遠不賺最後一個銅板，在房地產最火熱、別人為搶房擠破頭，他選擇急流勇退，賣掉一城又一城，至今累計套現人民幣1700多億元（244.3億美元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7333/3515409?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7333%2F3515409%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=E19L6z%2Bp8GfveTtRqWmKGcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3c65fed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7333/3515409?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"d528af9923f9dfeb98d977fb57c4fe6bae90756f","tid":926011,"uid":61257,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"+x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaf93fb6bd437296f65c625324a4bd73de0c2af","tid":926011,"uid":59283,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"撤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a7b641ae2d4deb8765324adcea5e8382216d56","tid":926011,"uid":51753,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4eaf93fb6bd437296f65c625324a4bd73de0c2af","tid":926011,"uid":59283,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"撤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c4247b21e650119f77d481875d0f0f627e774f","tid":926011,"uid":62815,"like":224,"dislike":3,"score":221,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"商業之神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解一個潮州佬做生意<br />\n可以擺脫過往中國富商嘅風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793c66fdcfb7fbf1c74e55a02c4038f2b3809732","tid":926011,"uid":73,"like":93,"dislike":2,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"領匯鳩接大陸資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284661f47d51a92f3403178064f88714ccdc3bf8","tid":926011,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"咁少"},{"pid":"43d2ede5a1ff72efeb886d02d6f97d429f4c86be","tid":926011,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf3b5c94693763459e3b6c2fd0c8216a3b5e212","tid":926011,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T0